features.text:
Bad Bad Potatoes..
In the Station orbiting the Silly Planet, the potato harvest has started! During quality control, 3,333 defective potatoes were picked out by the hard-working Space Inmates.

Everyone is calling these potatoes the PixelTots, and they are going on a rampage! Theyre running around stealing, and the latest reports say that theyre hiding and burning everyone's underwear, food, collectibles and more!

Catch these bad potatoes!!!

Artist Edition Potatoes
Artist Edition Potatoes will be auctioned on Ethereum as a special collection. 100% of the auction profit will be sent to the artist of the beautiful unique potato artwork.

Catch the PixelTots and become one with the Supreme Potato
3,333 Bad Bad PixelTots are hiding inside the Polygon blockchain. Each NFT is available to mint for 36 MATIC (about 0.02 ETH Polygon Network). There are more than 120 traits and each one of them is full of personality.  


We provide no promise other than this weird-ass art, PixelTots has the silliness youve been longing for. Come with us on a journey and become one with the Supreme Potato.
